Package com.fasterxml.jackson.dataformat.xml.deser

Class Summary
FromXmlParser JsonParser implementation that exposes XML structure as set of JSON events that can be used for data binding.
XmlBeanDeserializerModifier The main reason for a modifier is to support handling of 'wrapped' Collection types.
 

Enum Summary
FromXmlParser.Feature Enumeration that defines all togglable features for XML parsers
